{"tid":1559503,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"現階運動不應spin去港獨 因外國唔會撐 ［抗爭歌is not 國歌］","createTime":"2019-09-11T00:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T03:36:41.000Z","uid":160262,"like":29,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e7154ec575ce00c3741fa58b136bef1e28c920a4","tid":1559503,"uid":160262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:13:47.000Z","msg":"追究 黑警 依啲民生人道議題 好多外國人撐<br />\n相反港獨人地係無乜理由要支持香港<br />\n<br />\n避免稱抗爭歌為國歌<br />\n你定一首歌做國歌唔會有乜大幫<br />\n但係政府會放大港獨依個點 從而減少我地喺外國嘅支持<br />\n<br />\n政府之前已試過將場運動spin去港獨<br />\n林鄭：「光復香港 時代革命」<br />\n係因為各方面都有回應表示依句口號唔代表港獨<br />\n先無被spin走個重點<br />\n同埋你會見/聽到 「五大訴求 缺一不可」喺同時間跑出 我認為就係因為唔少人同我一樣諗法 就係唔想場抗爭spin咗做港獨<br />\n<br />\n老老實實 反送中 同 獨立 完完全全 兩樣野<br />\n我做文宣都係咁同人解釋 爭取支持<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c4f0e245ac515a24e8f7410c7a76b211989444","tid":1559503,"uid":160262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:14:00.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"ce263df754e631c07bf55462758e6894f9662c50","tid":1559503,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiW8u64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiW8u64.jpg&h=6e2a8a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558977</a>"},{"pid":"7fa04bce1bd1532d8e6d9b8c8937f9a1018162b6","tid":1559503,"uid":160262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:14:11.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"9cd57f2a5ce0d04b5b01d5abf338a45cc96d1f62","tid":1559503,"uid":160262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:14:50.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"b855048fd9e69034449ee4130f0e23bcef24c8a8","tid":1559503,"uid":88578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:14:59.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"ca368672c